# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEPLOYMENT VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Pre-Deployment Checks

Before deploying ui5-web or gateway changes, verify:

- [ ] **Base href set correctly** in build: `--base-href /ui5/`
- [ ] **Pre-gzip assets exist**: `find dist -name "*.js.gz" | wc -l` should be > 0
- [ ] **No absolute asset paths**: `grep -r '"/assets/' src/` should return 0 matches
- [ ] **publicPath is empty**: Check bundled main.js
- [ ] **i18n files present**: `ls dist/apps/workspace/assets/i18n/`
- [ ] **Environment config valid**: Check requireRealBackends, API URLs

## Post-Deployment Smoke Tests

After deployment, run these checks (adapt GATEWAY_URL):

```bash
export GATEWAY_URL=https://suite-gateway.c-054c570.kyma.ondemand.com

# 1. HTML with correct base href
curl -s "$GATEWAY_URL/ui5/" | grep -o '<base href="[^"]*"'
# Expected: <base href="/ui5/">

# 2. All JS bundles return 200
for f in main.js vendor.js runtime.js polyfills.js; do
  curl -sI "$GATEWAY_URL/ui5/$f" | head -1
done
# Expected: HTTP/2 200 for each

# 3. i18n files accessible
curl -sI "$GATEWAY_URL/ui5/assets/i18n/messages_en" | head -1
# Expected: HTTP/2 200

# 4. Check compression (Content-Encoding should be gzip)
curl -sI -H "Accept-Encoding: gzip" "$GATEWAY_URL/ui5/vendor.js" | grep -i content-encoding
# Expected: content-encoding: gzip (if fix deployed)

# 5. API health endpoints
curl -s "$GATEWAY_URL/api/v1/ui5/openai/health"
# Expected: {"status":"ok"} or similar

# 6. Check response time (should be < 3s for first byte)
curl -w "TTFB: %{time_starttransfer}s\n" -o /dev/null -s "$GATEWAY_URL/ui5/"
# Expected: TTFB < 3.0s
```

## Browser Verification (Manual)

For production deployments, ALWAYS verify in browser:

1. Open the URL in Chrome/Firefox
2. Open DevTools (F12) BEFORE loading page
3. Check Console tab - should have NO red errors
4. Check Network tab - all resources should be 200
5. Verify visual rendering occurs within 5 seconds
6. Click navigation elements to verify lazy loading works

