# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TROUBLESHOOTING DECISION TREE
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Blank Page Diagnosis

```
Page is blank
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв–є Check Network tab: Are JS bundles loading?
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в”њв”Ђв–є 404 errors в”Ђв”Ђв–є Check nginx config, base href, deployment
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в””в”Ђв–є All 200 в”Ђв”Ђв–є Continue below
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв–є Check Console tab: Any red errors?
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в”њв”Ђв–є Yes в”Ђв”Ђв–є Fix the specific error (see error patterns below)
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в””в”Ђв–є No errors в”Ђв”Ђв–є Check below
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв–є Check i18n loading: Network tab, filter "i18n"
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в”њв”Ђв–є 404 в”Ђв”Ђв–є KI-001: Fix path resolution
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в””в”Ђв–є 200 в”Ђв”Ђв–є Continue below
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв–є Check page source: Does it have Angular app-root?
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в”њв”Ђв–є No в”Ђв”Ђв–є HTML not served correctly, check nginx
    в”‚       в”‚
    в”‚       в””в”Ђв–є Yes, but empty в”Ђв”Ђв–є Angular bootstrap failed
    в”‚
    в””в”Ђв–є Check timing: How long before you gave up?
            в”‚
            в”њв”Ђв–є < 30s в”Ђв”Ђв–є KI-002: Compression issue, large bundles
            в”‚
            в””в”Ђв–є > 60s в”Ђв”Ђв–є Check network, may be connectivity issue
```

## Common Console Errors

| Error Pattern | Likely Cause | Fix |
|---------------|--------------|-----|
| `Failed to load module script` | CORS or path issue | Check base href, nginx CORS headers |
| `Cannot read property of undefined` | Initialization order | Check APP_INITIALIZER, async loading |
| `UI5 ... is not a constructor` | UI5 not loaded | Check UI5 asset paths |
| `Zone.js has detected that ZoneAwarePromise` | Zone.js conflict | Check for multiple zone.js imports |
| `NullInjectorError` | Missing provider | Check module imports |

