## Config File Ownership

| File | Owner | Review Required For |
|------|-------|---------------------|
| gateway/nginx.conf.template | Platform Team | Any proxy_pass, sub_filter changes |
| docker/nginx-suite-web.conf | UI5 Team | gzip, caching, routing changes |
| Dockerfile.suite-web | UI5 Team | Build steps, base image changes |
| app.config.ts | UI5 Team | Initialization, provider changes |

