# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CHANGE REVIEW CHECKLIST
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## For nginx Config Changes

- [ ] Tested locally with `docker compose up`
- [ ] Verified sub_filter rewrites work (check page source)
- [ ] Verified compression still works (check Content-Encoding header)
- [ ] Ran smoke-public-paths.sh against local gateway
- [ ] No new absolute paths introduced

## For Angular Build Changes

- [ ] Build completes without errors
- [ ] dist/ folder contains expected files
- [ ] No absolute paths in bundled JS (grep check)
- [ ] i18n files present in dist/assets/i18n/
- [ ] Pre-gzip files created (if Dockerfile updated)

## For Docker Image Changes

- [ ] Image builds successfully
- [ ] Health endpoint returns 200
- [ ] Static assets served with correct Content-Type
- [ ] gzip_static working (if configured)

